  <summary date="2017-01-12T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">IRGC Terrorist Sanctions Act of 2017

This bill directs the President to: (1) designate Iran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC) as a terrorist entity, (2) impose sanctions against the IRGC, and (3) report to Congress on the results of such sanctions.</summary>
